comments.body: Sorry for the delay (I've been away for a few days) - I've just added Egretta thula × tricolor (and a few other Egretta hybrids).
@nollster -- Egretta thula × tricolor should definitely be considered for addition. We'll need to ask @maxkirsch for help with this.
@d_kluza would this be candidate for added taxon?
It is definitely one of the Snowy Egret x Tricolors from the Portland area, but I wasn't sure how to note it here in iNaturalist.
